metadata.name: Syzygy III
metadata.description:
A strong emotion is an irresistible force, like that of a celestial event.

Composed of several studio photographs shot during the super blood moon of May 2021, this video piece features German method actor Lukas Olszewski. It also aims to raise awareness for frontotemporal dementia, a rare disease directly affecting Olszewski's young family.

25% goes to Deutsche Alzheimer Society.

Dimensions: 1760 x 2200
Duration: 00:10
